<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="/wiki/File:George_Monbiot.jpg" class="image" title="George Monbiot"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f6/George_Monbiot.jpg/220px-George_Monbiot.jpg" width="220" height="334" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:George_Monbiot.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
George Monbiot</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><b>George Joshua Richard Monbiot</b> (born 27 January 1963) is a <a href="/wiki/Journalist" title="Journalist">journalist</a>, <a href="/wiki/Columnist" title="Columnist">columnist</a>, author, <a href="/wiki/Academic" title="Academic" class="mw-redirect">academic</a>, and <a href="/wiki/Environmentalism" title="Environmentalism">environmental</a> and <a href="/wiki/Politics" title="Politics">political</a> <a href="/wiki/Activism" title="Activism">activist</a> in the United Kingdom who writes a weekly column for <i><a href="/wiki/The_Guardian" title="The Guardian">The Guardian</a></i> newspaper.</p>
